    // `a[i-1] >= a[i]` (this is the condition that stopped the first loop)
    // `a[i] >= ... >= a[n-1]` (non-increasing suffix)
    // So `a[j] <= ... <= a[i-1] >= a[i] >= ... >= a[n-1]`.
    // This is a mountain array with peak at `i-1` or `i`.
    // The peak is at `i-1` if `a[i-1] >= a[i]`.
    // The peak is at `i` if `a[i-1] < a[i]`.
